Package wellen

Class Module

java.lang.Object
wellen.Module
All Implemented Interfaces:
DSPNodeOutputSignal, Loopable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Track
public abstract class Module extends Object implements DSPNodeOutputSignal, Loopable
a module allows to compose complex DSP configurations. it is a container that may be managed by a Track.

a module must implement the method 

void output(Signal)
which supplies an audio signal and may implement the method 
void beat(int)
which can be used to receive beat events.

    • set_length

      public void set_length(int length)
      set length of a module loop. setting the length affects outpoint. e.g given an inpoint of 3, setting the length to 2 will set output to 4. note that outpoint is inclusive i.e a pattern from in- to outpoint of 3, 4, 5, … is generated.
      Parameters:
      length - set length of loop
